imdb.plot outline: For 125 years, Banamex has been a pioneer in implementing the Mexican financial system while serving the State, fostering all economic sectors, maintaining a significant presence in the international arena, and backing culture and education. For these reasons and more, it can be stated that more than just a bank, Banamex has been an institution key to national development.
imdb.title: 125 años del Banco Nacional de México
akas: 125 años del Banco Nacional de México (Mexico)
